{"tid":914521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 工作壓力爆煲 90後豪宅內服藥昏迷","createTime":"2018-11-24T11:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T11:07:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"907fab9ff8c0e0a48886c4bcc0260ad4a8b2d33f","tid":914521,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T11:06:04.000Z","msg":"周六（24日）凌晨約零時半，警方接獲何文田常盛街28號「皓畋」一單位的姓黎（29歲）男子報案，指懷疑其姓余（28歲）妻子服食過量止痛藥物，不省人事。<br />\n<br />\n救護員趕抵立即將女事主送往伊利沙伯醫院治理，當時她仍然陷於昏迷。消息稱，余女近日<span style=\"color: red;\">因為工作問題鬱鬱不歡</span>，警方調查後相信事件無可疑，案件列作「企圖自殺」處理。<br />\n<br />\n求助網站和熱線<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/262924/%E4%BD%95%E6%96%87%E7%94%B0%E5%B0%91%E5%A9%A6%E7%96%91%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E7%88%86%E7%85%B2-%E7%9A%93%E7%95%8B-%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85%E5%85%A7%E6%9C%8D%E8%97%A5%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F262924%2F%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%258A%259B%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2585%25B2-%25E7%259A%2593%25E7%2595%258B-%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E5%25AE%2585%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%259C%258D%25E8%2597%25A5%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7&d=pMSCnlU2dnyOAO5ZSdGKPMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=0f6fcb3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/262924/%E4%BD%95%E6%96%87%E7%94%B0%E5%B0%91%E5%A9%A6%E7%96%91%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B%E7%88%86%E7%85%B2-%E7%9A%93%E7%95%8B-%E8%B1%AA%E5%AE%85%E5%85%A7%E6%9C%8D%E8%97%A5%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7</a>"},{"pid":"8b39247ef6d90ca0f5ce749b2d8a41dd10afbb12","tid":914521,"uid":56097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T11:06:48.000Z","msg":"妻子rip"},{"pid":"6b8d73e0ecb532f4d004e0935f77529919521217","tid":914521,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T11:07:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0690466266f128da03f